    "For RETRO P-Tuning specifically, we hypothesis that P-Tuning's weaker ability in all RETRO model sizes could lie in architecture differences.",
    "In P-tuning, virtual tokens are intentionally prepended to the decoder's input, but they are not included in the retrieval encoder.",
    "Although they can influence the encoder through cross-attention, the impact might not be as direct or substantial as required.",
    "Alternatively, LoRA and Adapters are added to both encoder and decoder which explains their improved capabilities.",
    "4) The performance ceiling for PEFT-tuned models is notably higher for GPT than RETRO."
